article_title: Nonprofit ramps up healthcare signup efforts
article_text:
Novato, CA (94945)

Today

Areas of morning fog with some patchy drizzle. Cloudy skies early, then partly cloudy this afternoon. High 66F. Winds W at 10 to 20 mph..

Tonight

Partly cloudy this evening, then becoming cloudy after midnight. Areas of fog developing with patchy drizzle possible. Low near 50F. Winds W at 5 to 10 mph.
